    Protobuf enum opencannabis.products.PrerollFlag

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CONTAINS_TOBACCO
      Specifies that this product contains tobacco.
      FORTIFIED
      Specifies that this pre-rolled item is fortified with extracted cannabis products in some manner.
      FULL_FLOWER
      Specifies that this pre-rolled item is rolled with "full flower" buds, rather than trimmings, or other discarded cannabis from other production processes.
      HASH_INFUSED
      Specifies that this pre-rolled item is hash-infused.
      KIEF_INFUSED
      Specifies that this pre-rolled item is kief-infused.
      NO_PREROLL_FLAGS
      Specifies that no flags are set.
      UNRECOGNIZED
